---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Ida from "../assets/images/Ida.jpg";
---

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 px-5 mt-14 lg:mt-36">
  <div class="col-span-1">
    <h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl pb-4">About me</h3>
    <div class="mr-10 text-lg pb-6">
      <p>
        My creativity drives me to find innovative solutions to challenges. I am
        proactive, creative, and a strong team player capable of creating
        synergy across media platforms. <br /><br />
        I appreciate art, music, poetry, cooking, and engaging in all sensory experiences.
        I find great inspiration in nature and the people around me. I consider myself
        an empathetic, resourceful individual with a committed work ethic and a great
        sense of humor.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sm:block">
    <Image src={Ida} alt="Portrait" class="fade-in" />
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-1 md:ml-10">
    <h3 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl pb-4">Details</h3>
    <ul class="list-none text-lg mb-6 leading-loose">
      <li><strong>Full name:</strong> Ida Lærke Hallbæck-Andersen</li>
      <li><strong>Date of birth:</strong> November 14th, 1995</li>
      <li><strong>Location:</strong> Copenhagen, Denmark</li>
      <li><strong>Programme:</strong> APD in Multi Media Design</li>
      <li>
        <strong>Institution:</strong> KEA – Copenhagen School of Design and Technology
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  li {
    line-height: 200%;
  }
</style>
